data.description: MLS #270891  Now offering $10,000 for a rate buydown!  Welcome to your dream home! This magnificent 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom oasis offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort and entertainment. As you step inside, the open concept layout welcomes you, as the spacious living area seamlessly connects to the modern kitchen with sleek granite countertops. The large island serves as the perfect centerpiece for both meal prep and hosting unforgettable gatherings. Have plenty of space in the huge primary suite that features a large soaking tub and walk in closet. On the other side you will find two more generous sized bedrooms. For those who love to unwind and entertain outdoors, enjoy the covered patio and large hot tub (that stays!) with built in Bluetooth speakers. If you have been searching for the perfect combination of modern living and comfort, look no further!
